---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About Arthur Aizikovich — Copenhagen Photographer"
  description="Meet Arthur Aizikovich — Copenhagen-based photographer specialising in conference, wedding and event photography with an eye for genuine moments."
  locale="en"
>
  <article>
    <header class="page-header container">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>Arthur Aizikovich</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Copenhagen-based photographer specialising in conferences, weddings and events.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="bio container">
      <div class="bio-text">
        <p>
          I'm a photographer and founder of AA Media. My work is about capturing the moments that tell the story behind an event — the spontaneous glance during a keynote, the nerves before the bride walks in, the energy in the networking room.
        </p>
        <p>
          I've photographed everything from international tech conferences with 1,000+ attendees to intimate weddings and late-night venues. Every assignment starts from the same place: minimal disruption, maximum authenticity.
        </p>
        <p>
          Beyond photography I handle all post-production myself, delivering a curated selection of retouched images within the agreed deadline — typically 5–7 working days.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="bio-facts">
        <dl class="facts-list">
          <div class="fact">
            <dt>Based in</dt>
            <dd>Copenhagen, Denmark</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="fact">
            <dt>Availability</dt>
            <dd>Denmark + international assignments</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="fact">
            <dt>Languages</dt>
            <dd>Danish · English · Russian</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="fact">
            <dt>Turnaround</dt>
            <dd>5–7 working days</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="services-grid container">
      <h2 class="section-label">Specialities</h2>
      <ul class="services" role="list">
        <li class="service-item">
          <span class="service-index">01</span>
          <h3>Conference photography</h3>
          <p>Keynotes, panel discussions, networking and delegate portraits. Discreet, professional coverage of the full event.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="service-item">
          <span class="service-index">02</span>
          <h3>Wedding photography</h3>
          <p>Documentary-style coverage from preparations to reception. Warm tones, natural light and the moments that matter.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="service-item">
          <span class="service-index">03</span>
          <h3>Event photography</h3>
          <p>Product launches, galas, nightlife and cultural events. The energy in the image, not just the documentation.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="service-item">
          <span class="service-index">04</span>
          <h3>Portraits &amp; headshots</h3>
          <p>Corporate headshots and personal branding. Natural, professional images for LinkedIn, websites and press.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-strip container">
      <p class="cta-text">Ready to talk about your next project?</p>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="cta-btn">Book a call</a>
    </section>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding-block: var(--space-16) var(--space-12);
    max-width: var(--content-width);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-4);
  }

  .lead {
    margin-block-start: var(--space-6);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .bio {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-12);
    padding-block-end: var(--space-16);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .bio {
      grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
      gap: var(--space-16);
    }
  }

  .bio-text p {
    margin-block-end: var(--space-6);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .facts-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .fact dt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-1);
  }

  .fact dd {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .services-grid {
    padding-block: var(--space-16);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-8);
  }

  .services {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .services {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .service-item {
    padding-block-start: var(--space-6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .service-index {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-3);
  }

  .service-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-3);
  }

  .service-item p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .cta-strip {
    padding-block: var(--space-16);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-8);
    background: var(--color-text);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: background-color var(--transition-fast);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .cta-btn:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
